<br>
There are three ways to get to that safe spot from the Siren's Grotto Tunnel.<br>
<br>
1) Invis everyone and follow the ocean to the west all the way around.  Bad way because invis will drop and people will get attacked and split up.<br>
<br>
2) Just fight your way there along the edge killing the wolves and wurms along the way.  Just keep everyone together.  You will have to kill Yeldema once you get to the #9 area and then kill Hachaeva (#5) before you can move on.  Neither see invis but 95% of the time someone loses invis and the raid gets wiped by getting attacked without being ready.<br>
<br>
3)  Run yourself and a magician to the safe spot while invis and sow'd.  Easy with just two of you to get there while invis.  Then gate back and CoH everyone.<br>
<br>
I prefer #2.<br>
<br>
